object-pool provides header-only generic object pooling.

Usage:
    find_package(object-pool CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE object-pool::object-pool)

Example:
    #include <object-pool/object_pool.hpp>
    pool::object_pool<MyClass> my_pool(16, true);
    auto obj = my_pool.acquire();
    // obj is automatically returned to pool when shared_ptr refcount reaches 0
